## Git Workflow

**Branch Strategy**: `{{ main_branch }}`{% if staging_branch %} (production), `{{ staging_branch }}` (integration){% endif %}, `feature/*` (work branches)

{% if staging_branch %}
**Merge path**: `feature/*` → PR to `{{ staging_branch }}` → PR from `{{ staging_branch }}` to `{{ main_branch }}`. Never merge directly to `{{ main_branch }}`.
{% else %}
**Merge path**: `feature/*` → PR to `{{ main_branch }}`.
{% endif %}

> **Agents commit, humans push.** Create commits freely, but request user confirmation before pushing or merging.

